        </h1>
        <div class="\${classes.counter}">
            <\${Button} handleClick="\${({ props }) => props.handleIncrement}">
                count is \${({ props }) => props.count}
            </\${Button}>
        </div>
        <div class="\${classes.info}">
            <div class="\${classes.infoStack}">
                <p class="\${classes.infoDescription}">Pre-rendered static site with <a href="https://rasti.js.org" target="_blank">Rasti</a> + <a href="https://vite.dev" target="_blank">Vite</a> + <a href="https://expressjs.com" target="_blank">Express</a>, styled with <a href="https://cssfun.js.org" target="_blank">CSSFUN</a> (CSS-in-JS with light and dark themes). Development uses SSR; run <code>npm run build:static</code> to export configured URLs to static HTML under <code>dist/static</code>.</p>
                <div class="\${classes.infoIncludes}"><p>No optional extras included.</p></div>
                <p class="\${classes.infoHint}">Edit <code>src/App.js</code> and save to test HMR.</p>
